---
import { ArrowRight, CheckCircle2 } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-navy text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

            <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-brand-accent/20 text-brand-accent rounded-full text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
                    Specialty Capability
                </span>

                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
                    Kajabi Services
                </h2>

                <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    Kajabi is a specialist TheEduAssist capability. We provide comprehensive setup, migration, and management for learning businesses built on the Kajabi platform.
                </p>

                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
                    {[
                        "Course structure and setup",
                        "Websites and landing pages",
                        "Products, Offers, and checkout",
                        "Email and automations",
                        "Platform migration",
                        "Ongoing system support"
                    ].map(item => (
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent mr-3 mt-1 shrink-0" />
                            <span class="text-slate-300">{item}</span>
                        </li>
                    ))}
                </ul>

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <a href="/kajabi-services/" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-3 bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-md font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-accent transition-all shadow-md focus-ring hover-lift click-press">
                        Explore Kajabi Services
                        <ArrowRight class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" />
                    </a>
                    <a href="/book-free-kajabi-audit/" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 text-white rounded-md font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all border border-white/20 focus-ring hover-lift click-press">
                        Get a Kajabi Review
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-brand-primary/40 to-brand-accent/40 rounded-[2rem] blur-3xl transform -rotate-6"></div>
                <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-[2rem] relative backdrop-blur-sm">
                   <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-brand-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl">
                       <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-white"><path d="M12 2H2v10l9.29 9.29c.94.94 2.48.94 3.42 0l6.58-6.58c.94-.94.94-2.48 0-3.42L12 2Z"/><path d="M7 7h.01"/></svg>
                   </div>
                   <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Why Keep Kajabi Separate?</h3>
                   <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                       While we build custom eLearning and configure complex LMS environments, Kajabi requires a unique blend of instructional design and marketing technology setup.
                   </p>
                   <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                       We maintain a dedicated focus for our Kajabi clients to ensure their courses integrate perfectly with their sales systems.
                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
